Brand New Kitchen sink, and Faucet Sprayer with  water spout for pots! This house is ready to move in, no holes in walls from hanging pictures!!, Hardwoods in Great room, Breakfast area, Dining Room and Foyer. Large Fenced back yard, 4 Sides Brick, 3 bedrooms up, 2 with jack n jill bath. Large Bonus room, tons of storage space in basement. Underground Utilities. Walking distance to Cosby Lake, close to restaurants, grocery, and I-59. Beautiful home waiting for new family to love!! Bidets in master and half bath do not stay.
